## Prevent Memory Leaks

If the component unmounts before the fetch completes, setting state will cause a memory leak. Use a flag to ignore the result if unmounted:

```jsx
useEffect(() => {
  let ignore = false;
  fetchData().then(data => {
    if (!ignore) setData(data);
  });
  return () => { ignore = true; };
}, [deps]);
```
